content:
"Customers continue to see the value of XRP through significant cost-savings by eliminating the need to pre-fund international accounts. From Q4 2019 to Q1 2020, RippleNet’s On-Demand Liquidity (ODL) service tripled in transaction volume, and the dollar value transacted increased by more than 294%," said Ripple. <br data-v-f87c67ca="">
<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
The ODL solution leverages XRP to settle cross-border payments.&nbsp;
